Build requirements
==================
  libusb-1.0
  doxygen -- only if you want to build the documentation
  srecord (srec_cat) -- only if you change the microcode.rbf file (Microcode image).


Build instructions -- Linux (Debian Squeeze or later, Ubuntu 10.04 or later)
============================================================================
  sudo apt-get install libusb-1.0-0-dev
  make
  make install


To build the documentation:
===========================
  make docs

